                <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
                    <strong>UK company formation</strong> is the legal process of incorporating a private limited company with Companies House — the UK's official government business registry. The moment your application is approved, your business becomes a distinct legal entity, capable of entering contracts, owning assets, and employing staff entirely in its own name.
                </p>
                <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-8">
