                    <div class="p-6 bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl border border-gray-100">
                        <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 text-lg">Why Choose UK Company Formation?</h3>
                        <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-brand-blue font-bold mt-0.5">✓</span> <span><strong>Limited liability</strong> — personal assets are fully protected from business debts</span></li>
                            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-brand-blue font-bold mt-0.5">✓</span> <span><strong>Tax efficiency</strong> — pay Corporation Tax at 19%–25% instead of personal income tax rates up to 45%</span></li>
                            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-brand-blue font-bold mt-0.5">✓</span> <span><strong>Global credibility</strong> — UK companies are respected worldwide for contracts, payments, and partnerships</span></li>
                            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-brand-blue font-bold mt-0.5">✓</span> <span><strong>Access to banking</strong> — open accounts with Wise, Tide, Revolut, and traditional UK banks</span></li>
                            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-brand-blue font-bold mt-0.5">✓</span> <span><strong>Open to non-residents</strong> — any nationality can own and direct a UK Ltd company remotely</span></li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                    <div class="p-6 bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl border border-gray-100">
                        <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 text-lg">Legal Requirements for UK Ltd Registration</h3>
                        <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-brand-blue font-bold mt-0.5">→</span> <span>A unique company name (ending in "Limited" or "Ltd")</span></li>
